      • createMultiPageFiles

        public void createMultiPageFiles(java.lang.String ghostscriptPdfParameters,
                        java.lang.String batchInstanceIdentifier,
                        java.lang.String pdfOptimizationParams,
                        java.lang.String checkPDFExportProcess,
                        java.lang.String pluginName,
                        java.lang.String pdfOptimizationSwitch,
                        java.lang.String createMultipageFileType,
                        java.lang.String rspFileName,
                        java.lang.String iTextSearchablePDFType)
                          throws DCMAApplicationException
        This method takes the FolderToBeExported path and creates multi page tiff and PDF files based on the batch.xml file found in the folder.
        Parameters:
        ghostscriptPdfParameters - String ghost script pdf parameters.
        batchInstanceIdentifier - String batch instance identifier.
        pdfOptimizationParams - String pdf optimization parameters.
        checkPDFExportProcess - String pdf export process parameters.
        pluginName - String name of plugin.
        pdfOptimizationSwitch - String pdf optimization switch.
        createMultipageFileType - String file type for creating multipage files. Options: Tiff/PDF/Tiff and PDF.
        iTextSearchablePDFType - String IText searchable pdf type (Pdf or pdf Advanced).
        Throws:
        DCMAApplicationException - if any error occurs while creating multi page tiff and pdf.
